-- Simon Property Secures $4.6 Billion Loan to Finance Capital Shopping Offer
-- B y   J a m e s   C o n e
-- 2010-12-29T12:35:20Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-29/simon-property-secures-4-6-billion-loan-to-finance-capital-shopping-offer.html
Simon Property Group Inc. said it
reached agreement on financial terms of a loan facility of about
3 billion pounds, which would enable the company to satisfy in
full acceptances due under a firm offer for Capital Shopping
Centres Group Plc.  Simon said it has obtained the approval of its board for a
firm offer of 425 pence per CSC share and is “continuing its
efforts to seek engagement with the board of CSC.”   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James Cone at 
 jcone@bloomberg.net  